flowchart TD
  A[Creer facture] --> B[Valider donnees]
  B --> C[Calculer HT TVA TTC]
  C --> D[Generer numero sequentiel]
  D --> E[Generer code auth]
  E --> F[Generer QR]
  F --> G[Certifier / sceller]
